                  //-   .col.width-50: img(src='assets://images/stork-right.png')
        .section.city: .container
          h1 Built For the City
          p The Sprinter vans are standard vehicles that avoid many of the complications associated with the conversion of a recreational vehicle for use as a mobile medical unit. With a modest turn radius, a Sprinter van is easy to maneuver and park in a city. Our Stork Buses are space efficient, both inside and out. These vehicles are perfectly suited to sidewalk counseling. They provide the comfort and privacy to put a woman at ease and help your center demonstrate to her the love and compassion of Jesus.
        .bus-footer.align-center: .container
          h1 Why Go Mobile With Save The Storks?
          .row.columns
            .col.width-33
              .img: img(src='{bus.relationships(whygomobilecol1img,attachments).first.version(,)}')
              {bus.content.whygomobilecol1txt}
            .col.width-33.middle
              .img: img(src='{bus.relationships(whygomobilecol2img,attachments).first.version(,)}')
              {bus.content.whygomobilecol2txt}
            .col.width-33
              .img: img(src='{bus.relationships(whygomobilecol3img,attachments).first.version(,)}')
              {bus.content.whygomobilecol3txt}
